title: The Terminator: SkyNET [16:55] (RTA)
description: Shout outs to JAlbertH for really digging through this game and finding a bunch of strats and routing it! Really really happy that you did that because I've wanted to run this for years but never really had the patience to do the hard work myself. Very cool speedrun with some unique-ass tricks. I explain some stuff at the end of the video!
